articles.title: Dengue cases top 5.2 million in the Americas as outbreak passes yearly record, PAHO says - CNN
articles.description: Dengue cases are surging in the Americas, with cases reported topping 5.2 million as of this week, surpassing a yearly record set in 2023, according to the Pan American Health Organization (PAHO).
